!
#email config
!
#sntp client config
sntp-client
sntp-client server 0.pool.ntp.org port 123
sntp-client server 1.pool.ntp.org port 123
sntp-client server 2.pool.ntp.org port 123
sntp-client server 3.pool.ntp.org port 123
